OL,3,CUK Government 'letting down schools'
OL,5,FNorthern Ireland's education minister
OL,6,Fhas accused the UK Government of
OL,7,F"letting down" schools by withdrawing
OL,8,Ffunding for new buildings.
OL,10,FFunds for new buildings at a number of
OL,11,Fintegrated schools and shared
OL,12,Feducation campuses were ringfenced in
OL,13,Fthe Fresh Start Agreement in 2015.
OL,15,FLast week a Department of Education
OL,16,Fspokesperson said that #150million of
OL,17,Fthat funding is now no longer
OL,18,Favailable for the schools.
