OL,5,F"In addition, construction costs for
OL,6,Fthe Fresh Start projects have risen
OL,7,Fconsiderably in recent years. The
OL,8,Fremaining Fresh Start funding is
OL,9,Ftherefore sufficient only to cover
OL,10,Fthose projects currently in
OL,11,Fconstruction contract," he told MLAs.
OL,13,F"To give clarity to the remaining
OL,14,FFresh Start projects not yet in
OL,15,Fcontract, they will now be delivered
OL,16,Fwithin my department's conventional
OL,17,Fmajor works programme and will
OL,18,Fcontinue to advance in design and
OL,19,Fplanning.
