OL,5,FMr Givan insisted he had highlighted
OL,6,Fthe situation was a "real cause for
OL,7,Fconcern" from his first day in office
OL,8,Fearlier this month, and that the
OL,9,Ftreatment of the Fresh Start funding
OL,10,Fwas flagged before devolved government
OL,11,Fwas restored.
OL,13,FHe went on: "I am clear and my actions
OL,14,Fare clear. I have moved these schools
OL,15,Finto the conventional programme rather
OL,16,Fthan pausing, rather than cancelling
OL,17,Fthem, not because I've let them down
OL,18,Fbut because the Secretary of State and
OL,19,Fthe UK Government has let them down.
